<emphasis bold="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">New records.</emphasis>
Dibbīn Forest Reserve, ar Ruwayshid (
<figureCitation box="[690,803,1678,1703]" captionStart="FIGURE 10" captionStartId="12.[151,250,1423,1445]" captionTargetBox="[275,1307,228,1369]" captionTargetId="figure@12.[264,1323,193,1402]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURE 10. Distribution of the Asian garden dormouse, Eliomys melanurus." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1202799/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Figure 10</figureCitation>
